Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:26.62,jp.sub-ja,,0,0,0,,いつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.59,Style1,,0,0,0,,When did you take\Nnude photos of Haruhi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.28,jp.sub-ja,,0,0,0,,いつハルヒのヌードなんて撮ったぁぁぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.29,Style1,,0,0,0,,"Yes, that's the pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.86,jp.sub-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　そのポーズだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.30,Style1,,0,0,0,,That's a nice expression.
